(6, 2, 1, 4, 284, 2, 198, 'EHS-PARAMEDIC PROGRAM', NULL, 'salary', 40000, 50000, 'Will supervise and evaluate students during laboratory skills practice or assigned clinical rotations, instructs course components in areas of certification/licensure. Assists in evaluation and revision of course components presented. If working clinically, will plan and execute clinical experiences appropriate to course objectives and didactic course components.', 'Education:  High School diploma or equivalent required.  Nationally Registered paramedic and/or licensed Registered Nurse in Virginia.\r\n\r\nExperience:  Two (2) years of field EMS as a paramedic and/or clinical experience as an RN required.  Teaching experience preferred.\r\n\r\nOther Minimum Qualifications:  Must have the ability to communicate effectively verbally and in writing. Good understanding of educational principles and methodologies.', NULL, NULL, 0, '2017-06-26 00:29:36', '2017-06-26 00:29:36'),
