icans with Disabilities Acts (ADA and ADAAA), Virginia Western Community College will provide, if requested, reasonable accommodation to applicants in need of access to the application, interviewing and selection processes. Virginia Western is committed to Equal Opportunity\\/Affirmative Action and Diversity.\",\"user_id\":2,\"pay_min\":\"70000\",\"pay_max\":\"80000\",\"updated_at\":\"2017-06-26 05:54:10\",\"created_at\":\"2017-06-26 05:54:10\",\"id\":2,\"state\":{\"id\":1,\"name\":\"Texas\",\"short_name\":\"TX\",\"created_at\":\"2017-06-26 04:13:56\",\"updated_at\":\"2017-06-26 04:13:56\"},\"city\":{\"id\":5,\"state_id\":1,\"name\":\"Fort Worth\",\"created_at\":\"2017-06-26 04:13:56\",\"updated_at\":\"2017-06-26 04:13:56\"}}}', NULL, '2017-06-26 00:24:10', '2017-06-26 00:24:10'),
